### GitHub Discussions API 测试文件

### 获取讨论列表
GET {{host}}/api/GitHubDiscussions/microsoft/vscode?first=10&orderBy=UPDATED_AT&direction=DESC
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 根据编号获取讨论详情
GET {{host}}/api/GitHubDiscussions/microsoft/vscode/123
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 根据ID获取讨论详情
GET {{host}}/api/GitHubDiscussions/by-id/D_kwDOAJtVws4ASy-x
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 创建新讨论
POST {{host}}/api/GitHubDiscussions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "repositoryId": "MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnkxNjIzODg0NQ==",
  "title": "How to implement custom syntax highlighting?",
  "body": "I'm trying to add custom syntax highlighting for a new language. What's the best approach?",
  "categoryId": "DIC_kwDOAJtVws4CL3RI"
}

### 更新讨论
PUT {{host}}/api/GitHubDiscussions/D_kwDOAJtVws4ASy-x
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated: How to implement custom syntax highlighting?",
  "body": "I'm trying to add custom syntax highlighting for a new language. What's the best approach? Updated content..."
}

### 删除讨论
DELETE {{host}}/api/GitHubDiscussions/D_kwDOAJtVws4ASy-x
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 锁定讨论
POST {{host}}/api/GitHubDiscussions/D_kwDOAJtVws4ASy-x/lock
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

"SPAM"

### 解锁讨论
POST {{host}}/api/GitHubDiscussions/D_kwDOAJtVws4ASy-x/unlock
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 为讨论点赞
POST {{host}}/api/GitHubDiscussions/D_kwDOAJtVws4ASy-x/upvote
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 取消讨论点赞
DELETE {{host}}/api/GitHubDiscussions/D_kwDOAJtVws4ASy-x/upvote
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 获取讨论评论
GET {{host}}/api/GitHubDiscussions/D_kwDOAJtVws4ASy-x/comments?first=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 创建讨论评论
POST {{host}}/api/GitHubDiscussions/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "discussionId": "D_kwDOAJtVws4ASy-x",
  "body": "Great question! Here's how you can implement custom syntax highlighting..."
}

### 创建回复评论
POST {{host}}/api/GitHubDiscussions/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "discussionId": "D_kwDOAJtVws4ASy-x",
  "body": "I agree with the previous comment. Additionally...",
  "replyToId": "DC_kwDOAJtVws4AZJm5A"
}

### 更新讨论评论
PUT {{host}}/api/GitHubDiscussions/comments/DC_kwDOAJtVws4AZJm5A
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "Updated comment: Great question! Here's how you can implement custom syntax highlighting..."
}

### 删除讨论评论
DELETE {{host}}/api/GitHubDiscussions/comments/DC_kwDOAJtVws4AZJm5A
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 为评论点赞
POST {{host}}/api/GitHubDiscussions/comments/DC_kwDOAJtVws4AZJm5A/upvote
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 取消评论点赞
DELETE {{host}}/api/GitHubDiscussions/comments/DC_kwDOAJtVws4AZJm5A/upvote
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 标记评论为答案
POST {{host}}/api/GitHubDiscussions/comments/DC_kwDOAJtVws4AZJm5A/mark-as-answer
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 取消标记评论为答案
POST {{host}}/api/GitHubDiscussions/comments/DC_kwDOAJtVws4AZJm5A/unmark-as-answer
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 获取讨论分类列表
GET {{host}}/api/GitHubDiscussions/microsoft/vscode/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 根据ID获取讨论分类详情
GET {{host}}/api/GitHubDiscussions/categories/DIC_kwDOAJtVws4CL3RI
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 创建讨论分类
POST {{host}}/api/GitHubDiscussions/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "repositoryId": "MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnkxNjIzODg0NQ==",
  "name": "Extensions",
  "description": "Questions and discussions about VS Code extensions",
  "emoji": "🧩",
  "isAnswerable": true
}

### 更新讨论分类
PUT {{host}}/api/GitHubDiscussions/categories/DIC_kwDOAJtVws4CL3RI
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Extension Development",
  "description": "Updated: Questions and discussions about VS Code extension development",
  "emoji": "🔧"
}

### 删除讨论分类
DELETE {{host}}/api/GitHubDiscussions/categories/DIC_kwDOAJtVws4CL3RI
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 变量定义（在文件顶部）
@host = http://localhost:5000
@token = your_github_token_here
